      "content": "i dont even know why im typing this. everything just feels... heavy. like i've spent 5 years building this version of myself around my research and now that the funding is gone and the lab is basically shutting down, there's nothing left. i'm just so incredibly tired of fighting for a life that doesn't even feel like mine anymore. i just want the noise to stop.",
